<center><lj-cut text="ISLAVERSE: preplotting mixer"></center><lj-raw><div style="margin:0 auto;width:550px;font-family:helvetica,arial,sans-serif;text-align:justify;line-height:1.7;font-size:13px;">

Howdy, everybody! As I prep for the Islaverse plot, I wanted to go ahead and drop some ~spoilies~ in your lap before we go live. More specifically, I wanted to share with you the planned universes and split-off groups for the plot so that you can have the opportunity to preplan some fun and possible drama along the way. Additionally, if you have any ideas or wants from the upcoming plot that I can offer, just let me know and I'll (try!) to fit it in.<br><br>

	<!--TITLE-->
	<div style="text-align:center;font-family:arial black,gadget,sans-serif;color:#688985;font-size:22px;line-height:1;">
		ISLAVERSES
		<div style="margin:5px auto 20px auto;width:80px;height:4px;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.1);"></div>
	</div>

	<!--UNIVERSE 1-->
	<blockquote style="min-height:50px;margin:0 0 40px 0;padding:15px 15px 15px 70px;background:#fff;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">
		<img src="https://www.insanejournal.com/userpic/40396605/4314167" style="width:70px;height:70px;padding:7px;background:linear-gradient(to left bottom,#fff 70%,#A8D4CE 70%);border-bottom:7px solid #fff;float:left;margin:-40px 0 0 -90px;">
		<b style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#688985;display:block;">UNIVERSE 1: DOPPELGANGERS</b>
		This is the closest adjacent universe to the current LB one, which is basically... your evil twin. Think of it as the doppelganger universe, where it's basically you but with an evil mustache. Or a good mustache, if your present self is EVILLLLLLL. You can even change the gender of your person if you want, just because like... it's a construct but if you feel like your eViL tWiN would actually be a different gender, go off bitch.
	</blockquote>

	<!--UNIVERSE 2-->
	<blockquote style="min-height:50px;margin:0 0 40px 0;padding:15px 15px 15px 70px;background:#fff;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">
		<img src="https://www.insanejournal.com/userpic/40396410/4314167" style="width:70px;height:70px;padding:7px;background:linear-gradient(to left bottom,#fff 70%,#A8D4CE 70%);border-bottom:7px solid #fff;float:left;margin:-40px 0 0 -90px;">
		<b style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#688985;display:block;">UNIVERSE 2: ADULTHOOD BLOWS</b>
		This universe? Everything, mostly, is the same... except you developed magic when you were an adult, and a fair amount of your sparkly teen dreams were dashed.<br>
		Which is to say: this is our Original Adult Characters AU, if you transferred your character from a previous game. If your character is original to Looking Back, think about what their life would be like if they were an adult and also shit got really HBO gritty.
	</blockquote>
  
  	<!--UNIVERSE 3-->
	<blockquote style="min-height:50px;margin:0 0 40px 0;padding:15px 15px 15px 70px;background:#fff;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">
		<img src="https://www.insanejournal.com/userpic/40396629/4314167" style="width:70px;height:70px;padding:7px;background:linear-gradient(to left bottom,#fff 70%,#A8D4CE 70%);border-bottom:7px solid #fff;float:left;margin:-40px 0 0 -90px;">
		<b style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#688985;display:block;">UNIVERSE 3: THE FINAL FRONTIER</b>
		Welcome to Station 573-08B75, more colloqually known as Andromeda University! Here, humanoids of all types gather to engage in collegiate study, enjoy an anti-gravity keg stand at the Kappa Kappa Psi inter-species fraternity, and enjoy the best years of their lives! You know, in between all of the pirate raids.<br>
		Your character's AU dopp here is in their 20s, and if you want to change their sPeCiEs, go wild. Or just have them be themselves but 5 years older and shit. Like, it's up to you.
	</blockquote>
  
  	<!--UNIVERSE 4-->
	<blockquote style="min-height:50px;margin:0 0 40px 0;padding:15px 15px 15px 70px;background:#fff;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">
		<img src="https://www.insanejournal.com/userpic/40396633/4314167" style="width:70px;height:70px;padding:7px;background:linear-gradient(to left bottom,#fff 70%,#A8D4CE 70%);border-bottom:7px solid #fff;float:left;margin:-40px 0 0 -90px;">
		<b style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#688985;display:block;">UNIVERSE 4: BACK IN TIME</b>
		When the mist clears in this universe, it's pretty evident that it's familiar in a way you can't quite place a finger on. More specifically, you've... BEEN here before. Welcome to the world before the Green Flash, friends. Here there be past lives.<br>
		<u>NOTE</u>: if your character doesn't have a past life but you want your character to encounter someone, please feel free to improvise by having a copy of that person do whatever you wish, be in a shifter pack, etc.!
	</blockquote>
  
